  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick pan or skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add 1 tsp of vegetable oil and swirl to coat the pan.",
    "Add the bulgur and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring frequently, until lightly toasted.",
    "Add the Korean chili flakes, vegan mayo, and 1/4 tsp of salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the cucumber, red bell pepper, carrots, and green onions. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the ssam wrap and cook for 1-2 minutes, flipping halfway through, until slightly crispy.",
    "Transfer the wrap to a plate and top with the bulgur mixture, raspberry jam, and cilantro.",
    "If using cornstarch, sprinkle on top of the bulgur mixture.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
